title: Prison of Perfection || EP: 102
description:
Hey Rehabbers,
I just want you to know that you don't have to live in the prison of perfection anymore. So many people allow external expectations to put them in an internal depression. I hope this episode helps you to be more comfortable in your "humanness."
Please hit me up on IG (@TrentShelton) with your biggest takeaways and please share this with someone who could use it.
